<li>Rorty, A.O., "The Social and Political Sources of Akrasia", <i>Ethics</i>, Vol.107, No.4, (July 1997), pp.644–657.</li>
<li>Rorty, A.O. (1980). "Where Does the Akratic Break Take Place?" <i>Australasian Journal of</i></li>
</ul>
<p>Philosophy <i>58, pp. 333–46.</i></p>
